gw.bizrules.databuilder

Class RuleUpdateBuilder<R extends Rule,H extends RuleHead,B extends RuleUpdateBuilder<R,H,B,U>,U extends RuleBuilder<R,U>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.bizrules.databuilder.RuleUpdateBuilder<R,H,B,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - Rule subtype
    H - RuleHead subtype for Rule subtype
    B - Specific concrete subtype of this superclass
    U - Concrete builder type for specific Rule subtype

    public abstract class RuleUpdateBuilder<R extends Rule,H extends RuleHead,B extends RuleUpdateBuilder<R,H,B,U>,U extends RuleBuilder<R,U>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines the abstract superclass for concrete subtype builders of a RuleHead with an updated Rule after taking in an existing RuleHead. This is not a standard DataBuilder.
